other info that might help us debug this:

 Possible unsafe locking scenario:

       CPU0                    CPU1
       ----                    ----
  lock(&(&rdev->notifier)->rwsem);
                               lock(&ihid_goodix->regulator_mutex);
                               lock(&(&rdev->notifier)->rwsem);
  lock(&ihid_goodix->regulator_mutex);

 *** DEADLOCK ***

